Pablo Yamild Rosiles Loeza

**For english click here

Biografa

Profesional con experiencia en gestin de equipos, comunicacin cientfica, transferencia de tecnologa y genmica. Miembro de la RNA society. Pertenec al programa Talentum universidad y Shaping Horizons, organizado por el CIDE y la Universidad de Cambridge, respectivamente. En 2018, colabor en la organizacin y logstica de la Segunda Cumbre de Lderes Latinoamericanos en Biotecnologa de Allbiotech, donde posteriormente me desempe como Co-Coordinador de Polticas Pblicas. Actualmente curso el programa de maestra en biotecnologa de plantas en el Cinvestav donde me desempeo en el laboratorio de RNA regulatorio analizando marcas de cromatina en RNAs largos no codificantes.

Resume in english

Bio

Professional with experience in team management, scientific communication, technology transfer and genomics. Member of the RNA society. I belonged to the Talentum university program and Shaping Horizons, organized by CIDE and Cambridge University, respectively. In 2018, I collaborated in the organization and logistics of the Second Summit of Latin American Leaders in Biotechnology of Allbiotech, where I later served as Co-Coordinator of Public Policy. I am currently pursuing a Masters program in plant biotechnology at Cinvestav where I work in the regulatory RNA lab analyzing chromatin marks in long non-coding RNAs.
